name: Fish Fish Fang Fang - NEW RELEASE
name_original: Fish Fish Fang Fang - NEW RELEASE
description:
You start out as a tiny fish in a vast and endless ocean!
Can you eat and grow your way up to the top of the food chain, until you're able to devour the monster that frightens the entire submarine world?

Fish Fish Fang Fang is a  decorated, fun and colorful fish eater game, playable on computer and phone in your browser!

Enjoy!
